rows.label: tlk70000053_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm a bit more used to it now, but
it was hard for me to adapt to
giving instructions to people.

rows.label: tlk70000053_04_msg0002
rows.name:
When you're on the battlefield,
you have to make snap decisions
and judgments. That takes guts.

rows.label: tlk70000053_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It's terrifying to think that
your own misjudgment could
lead to someone's death.

rows.label: tlk70000053_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Adel-sama's strength helped me
trust in myself. It always seems
like he knows just what to do.
